org.apache.archiva.redback.keys

Interface AuthenticationKey

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    JpaAuthenticationKey, MemoryAuthenticationKey

    public interface AuthenticationKey
    AuthenticationKey is an object representing a key established to automatically authenticate a user without the user providing typical login credentials.
    Author:
    Joakim Erdfelt
